sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant K8S as Kubernetes API
    participant KSC as KServe Controller
    participant S3 as S3/Minio
    participant Pod as Model Server Pod
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway
    participant Router as KServe Router
    participant Trans as Transformer
    participant Pred as Predictor
    participant Expl as Explainer
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over Client,KSC: Flow 1: Model Deployment
    Client->>K8S: Create InferenceService (6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3)
    K8S-->>Client: 201 Created
    KSC->>K8S: Watch InferenceService
    KSC->>K8S: Create Deployment (6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3)
    K8S->>Pod: Start Pod
    Pod->>S3: Download model (443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+ AWS SigV4)
    S3-->>Pod: Model artifacts
    Pod->>Pod: Load model into memory
    Pod-->>KSC: Ready

    Note over Client,Expl: Flow 2: Inference Request (HTTP)
    Client->>Istio: POST /v1/models/{name}:predict (443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+)
    Istio->>Router: Forward request (8080/TCP HTTP mTLS)
    Router->>Trans: Route to transformer (8080/TCP HTTP mTLS)
    Trans->>Trans: Transform input
    Trans->>Pred: Forward to predictor (8080/TCP HTTP mTLS)
    Pred->>Pred: Run inference
    Pred->>Expl: Get explanation (8080/TCP HTTP mTLS)
    Expl->>Expl: Generate explanation
    Expl-->>Pred: Explanation result
    Pred-->>Trans: Prediction result
    Trans-->>Router: Transformed result
    Router-->>Istio: Response
    Istio-->>Client: 200 OK with prediction

    Note over Client,Pred: Flow 3: LLM Inference Request (OpenAI API)
    Client->>Istio: POST /v1/chat/completions (443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+)
    Istio->>Pred: Route to vLLM service (8080/TCP HTTP mTLS)
    Pred->>Pred: GPU inference + KV cache
    Pred-->>Istio: Streaming response
    Istio-->>Client: 200 OK with chat completion

    Note over Prom,KSC: Flow 4: Metrics Collection
    Prom->>Pred: Scrape /metrics (8080/TCP HTTP TLS 1.2+)
    Pred-->>Prom: Model metrics
    Prom->>Istio: Scrape /metrics (15090/TCP HTTP)
    Istio-->>Prom: Envoy metrics
    Prom->>KSC: Scrape /metrics (8080/TCP HTTP)
    KSC-->>Prom: Controller metrics
